{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Survive the evil spirits within the manor in this point-and-click horror adventure. Solve puzzles, meet spooky characters, and discover the mystery behind the Riddlewood family. Explore all the rooms of this haunted mansion, but remember, don\u2019t play with dolls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019550/extras/RiddlewoodManor_01.gif?t=1739849262\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019550/extras/RM_Description_Header_01.png?t=1739849262\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Venture through the shadowy corridors of the manor, where secrets await at every turn. From crafting a breakfast with unappetizing pig parts to assembling a s\u00e9ance board with hidden clues, each puzzle you uncover brings you closer to the tragic story of the Riddlewoods.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019550/extras/RiddlewoodManor_02.gif?t=1739849262\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019550/extras/RM_Description_Header_02.png?t=1739849262\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Riddlewood Manor blends horror and whimsy, providing an experience nostalgic of amusement park rides and Saturday morning cartoons. Each eerie room of the gothic mansion oozes dark charm, balancing moments of terror with the absurd. Comfort an eccentric dragon, feed a derpy chicken, and be wary of a sinister doll.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019550/extras/RiddlewoodManor_03.gif?t=1739849262\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019550/extras/RM_Description_Header_03.png?t=1739849262\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On a mission to purify the evil within the manor beneath the crimson sky, you\u2019ll find yourself in an atmosphere both mysterious and macabre. Brave the sudden frights as you navigate through the ghostly halls. Be careful, death awaits with just one misstep. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019550/extras/RM_Description_Header_04.png?t=1739849262\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A spooky point-and-click horror adventure </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the many rooms and secrets of Riddlewood Manor </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet strange characters, from a hungry chicken to a demonic doll </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solve a haunted house filled with intriguing puzzles </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience a charmingly dark narrative </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plenty of jump scares. BOO!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Peanut Button is an independent game studio founded by brothers Asaf Geva and Eyal Geva. The studio is known for <i>The Secret of Retropolis</i>, the critically acclaimed VR game and series. Riddlewood Manor is inspired by <i>Five Nights of Freddy\u2019s</i>, <i>Poppy Playtime</i>, and the <i>Rusty Lake</i> series.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3019550?t=1739849262","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019550/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739849262","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019550/298ebe11916bbfe1038b13d56d299adff1fd1150/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=173984926